Class BuildMenuFinishedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.web.events.BuildMenuFinishedEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class BuildMenuFinishedEvent
extends Object
implements NamedAcrossEvent
    Event fired by the MenuFactory whenever a menu has been build, sorted and the corresponding item has been selected. Can be used to modify the menu after build has completed.
